# Mutable runtime state — transcript DB, cron jobs, live memory + runtime skills.
# Lives under STATE_DIR (default bot/.state locally; a persistent volume in production).
# The repo's memory/*.md are SEEDS only; the bot writes the copies under STATE_DIR.
bot/.state/

